    <implementation-summary>
      Implemented email export using Microsoft Graph API for sending emails
      from the user's mailbox (OBO flow). The implementation is integrated
      directly into the BFF API following ADR-001.

      Implementation Details:

      1. EmailExportService.cs (NEW):
         - Location: src/server/api/Sprk.Bff.Api/Services/Ai/Export/
         - Implements IExportService for ExportFormat.Email
         - Uses IGraphClientFactory.ForUserAsync() for OBO authentication
         - Sends via /me/sendMail Graph API endpoint
         - Returns action-based result with Metadata (not FileBytes)

      2. HTML Email Template:
         - Professional styling with Spaarke branding (#0078D4)
         - Executive Summary section
         - Analysis Content with paragraph parsing
         - Entities table (Organizations, People, Dates, Amounts, References)
         - Clauses table with risk level color coding
         - Footer with generation info

      3. Attachment Support:
         - Optional DOCX or PDF attachments
         - Uses Lazy resolution to avoid circular dependency
         - Generates attachment using existing DocxExportService/PdfExportService
         - Uses FileAttachment with Base64-encoded content

      4. ExportFileResult Extensions:
         - Added Metadata dictionary for action-based exports
         - Added OkAction() factory method

      5. Orchestration Integration:
         - Updated AnalysisOrchestrationService.ExportAnalysisAsync()
         - Extracts email metadata (Recipients, Subject, SentAt)
         - Returns formatted status message

      Configuration (AnalysisOptions.cs):
      - EnableEmailExport - Feature flag (default: false)

      Files Created:
      - src/server/api/Sprk.Bff.Api/Services/Ai/Export/EmailExportService.cs
      - tests/unit/Sprk.Bff.Api.Tests/Services/Ai/EmailExportServiceTests.cs

      Files Modified:
      - src/server/api/Sprk.Bff.Api/Services/Ai/Export/IExportService.cs (added Metadata, OkAction)
      - src/server/api/Sprk.Bff.Api/Services/Ai/AnalysisOrchestrationService.cs (email handling)
      - src/server/api/Sprk.Bff.Api/Program.cs (IHttpContextAccessor, EmailExportService registration)

      Note: Email is sent directly via Graph API (from user's Outlook mailbox),
      not via Dataverse email activity. Dataverse integration can be added later
      if needed for tracking/workflow purposes.
    </implementation-summary>
